Use the cast button in the lower left to cast spells. Use those spells to explore the tiny island.

Spells cost mana to cast.

Some spells, like summons, also have an upkeep cost which you have to pay mana for every turn.

Your mana earned per turn is a function of your current power. You can spend your power on mana production or on researching new spells."
